Name: Game-Ready Assets
About the game: Game-Ready Assets is a content collection made for gamedevelopers. Content comprises source FBX and texture files. It has more than 500 models, textures and materials. We developed easy-to-use application to browse, view and download any model you need. Also we've prepared a special large free collection for you! Every collection will often be updated with new models and model-packs. Collections list will be expanded in course of time! List of Packages: Urban Interior Props Pack Ancient Catacombs Morgue Props Pack Old-School Props Pack Sci-Fi Textures Pack (with props) FREE Big Furniture Pack FREE Music Pack Blood Textures vol.1-2 Spiderweb Pack Lockers Pack vol.1 Road Pack Rocks Pack FREE Turets Pack FREE Books Pack Mummy Pack Industrial Textures Pack Old Wine Bottles Pack In Development Game-Ready - Monsters Collection Game-Ready - Textures/Materials Collection Game-Ready - Sound/Music Collection
